  "description": "Biomechanical: Aquatic Morphus table (Nightbane Survival Guide, WB5, pp. 83–84). Nightbane with this feature often feel a need to explore the world, especially beneath the waves. All rows grant Swimming at 80%, underwater breathing for 2D6+20 minutes per immersion (with or without air tanks present), and depth tolerance of 1,000 feet (305 m) unless a row states otherwise.",
